{"tid":40162,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"可怕的殖民情況","createTime":"2016-12-15T04:34:47.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-15T11:55:23.000Z","uid":30582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9c8adeaea7ec08d003e7b4abd16af51aa5f7c159","tid":40162,"uid":30582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T04:34:47.000Z","msg":"啲中國人食飯時硬係不停錦講嘢。真係討厭。成間老麥都係國語。依家香港既中國殖民已經可以消滅香港人了。真係可怕。"},{"pid":"3baa2baa0f30d99732789d0d935921e44c17b407","tid":40162,"uid":20357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T04:57:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲中國人食飯時硬係不停錦講嘢。真係討厭。成間老麥都係國語。依家香港既中國殖民已經可以消滅香港人了。真係可怕。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幼稚園，小學，連中學生都講普通話先可怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前見到一班中學生都係講普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5f662d0361a4ebf551b104727bd00d8e025d824","tid":40162,"uid":30582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T11:19:44.000Z","msg":"我都見過。幾個。好似係小學生。忘記了是在麥記定係大快活。<br />\n當時真係幾乎在心裏哭泣。"},{"pid":"747a25f6ced8bc732239cfdbab784dd46d789e0f","tid":40162,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T11:55:23.000Z","msg":"而家先知?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}